日示威中，已有警務人員被鐳射光照射後感不適甚至受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=358210&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358210%26refer%3DShare&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2BvxPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=db98a4c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D358210%26refer%3DShare&h=ea2dd3ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=358210&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"2d73f9b0bdca8a67bc80e341d3c1d00b3fe10340","tid":1423383,"uid":211565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:28:07.000Z","msg":"工會集體自首未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1a274a9846fc6f420730ad678ab31ebc3a5b8d0","tid":1423383,"uid":53413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:29:33.000Z","msg":"仆街啦<br />\n墨王點開墨啊"},{"pid":"f073f207c4a60d752e14ab4be20dd848e65c9059","tid":1423383,"uid":53413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:30:42.000Z","msg":"大獲<br />\n聽日又要用雷射做平水<br />\n會唔會犯左法<br />\n同老細講可唔可以唔做架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa01e3bf5edf3d7355b3554c6ed523727dc9d71f","tid":1423383,"uid":296072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d73f9b0bdca8a67bc80e341d3c1d00b3fe10340","tid":1423383,"uid":211565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:28:07.000Z","msg":"工會集體自首未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:36:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>各個工會帶頭自首吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嗱! 唔自首就告發佢哋㗎!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"0430f01e2e15cb1b052cd417033a1169e63835a9","tid":1423383,"uid":296072,"lik